Package: Exception
Type: Package
Title: Classed exception object hierarchy
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Stuart R. Jeffers
Maintainer: Stuart R. Jeffers <srjefferys@gmail.com>
Description: Provides classed Exception objects with a pre-defined hierarchy
 of classes. This allows catching exceptions in a nested way by using a
 class or parent class name with try-catch.
